David Cole visited Auschwitz in 1992. He paid extra for a personal tour, and he wore his yarmulke to make sure everybody knew he was Jewish. He made a video about the contradictory aspects of the Holocaust. The JDL reportedly threatened to kill him. The Holocaust is a significant part of human history, and it is still affecting our lives. We have a right to learn about it. Don&amp;#039;t be intimidated! If Jews can investigate the Holocaust, so can goyim! 
